- "sailors" metaphorically refers to the users involved in projects;
- "cast their anchors" metaphorically means being involved or collaborating;
- "waves of ongoing voyages" refers to projects with an 'active' status;
- "calm of past adventures" refers to projects with a 'completed' status.
